# Local state (secrets + per-machine data) — these live in the runtime
# data dir (~/.local/share/.whatsapp-rs), never in the repo tree.
# The leading `/.whatsapp-rs/` scope keeps us from matching `src/messages/`.
/.whatsapp-rs/
/device_cache.json
**/creds.json
**/sessions.json
**/pre-keys/
**/daemon.json
**/app-state-keys.json
**/app-state/

